{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "4a228c3b-e8ca-4832-8159-46512b559525", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/4a228c3b-e8ca-4832-8159-46512b559525@3.pkg/1772602024996/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602025790", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/4a228c3b-e8ca-4832-8159-46512b559525@3.pkg/1772602024996/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602025790"}, "identifier": "4a228c3b-e8ca-4832-8159-46512b559525", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;此头须向国门悬&rdquo;中的&ldquo;须&rdquo;是&ldquo;必须&rdquo;的意思,说明诗人即使死了也要一心关注革命,想亲眼看到同志们怎样取得战斗的胜利,表现出诗人视死如归的革命气概和坚信革命必胜的信念。</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>对下列诗句中的词语分析不恰当的一项是(　　)</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "对下列诗句中的词语分析不恰当的一项是(　　)", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/4a228c3b-e8ca-4832-8159-46512b559525@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754282798872", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;旌旗十万斩阎罗&rdquo;中的&ldquo;斩&rdquo;字寓指力度强,速度快,果断干脆,有居高临下的气势,强烈抒发了作者誓与反动派血战到底的决心。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;此头须向国门悬&rdquo;中的&ldquo;须&rdquo;是&ldquo;必须&rdquo;的意思,写出了作者的无奈、伤悲之情。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;捷报飞来当纸钱&rdquo;中的&ldquo;飞&rdquo;字暗含轻快、欢欣、联翩而至之意,富有生命力和感情色彩,抒发了作者的革命乐观主义精神。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;取义成仁今日事&rdquo;中的&ldquo;取义成仁&rdquo;可理解为&ldquo;舍生取义&rdquo;&ldquo;杀身成仁&rdquo;,表现了作者为了人民的解放事业而勇于牺牲的无产阶级革命精神。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>对下列诗句中的词语分析不恰当的一项是(　　)</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79